---
// distribution-network.astro - About: Distribution Network Detail Page
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Distribution Network | About | Sosun Fihaara"
  description="Examine Sosun Fihaara's archipelagic logistics infrastructure and dry/cold supply lines throughout Maldivian atolls."
>
  <main class="bg-[#F6F2E8] py-20 min-h-screen pt-28">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-5">
      <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
      <div class="mb-6 font-body text-xs text-[#566159] uppercase tracking-wider">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#00663B] no-underline">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp;
        <a href="/about" class="hover:text-[#00663B] no-underline">About</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp;
        <span class="text-[#18231D]">Distribution Network</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-[#D8D4C9] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm mb-12">
        <div class="p-8 lg:p-12">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-[#DDEBE2] text-[#00663B] px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
            Operations &amp; Infrastructure
          </span>

          <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-[#18231D] leading-tight mt-4 mb-6" style="font-size: var(--type-h2);">
            Our Distribution Infrastructure
          </h1>

          <div class="prose font-body text-base text-[#18231D] leading-relaxed max-w-none mb-8">
            <p class="mb-6">
              Distributing fast-moving consumer goods across 20 atolls and hundreds of dispersed islands requires structured logistics. Sosun Fihaara operates a synchronized supply line consisting of key harbor locations, bulk storage facilities, and archipelagic sea routes.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-[#18231D] mt-8 mb-3">1. Central Warehousing (Malé Hub)</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our central warehouses in the capital region act as the initial collection point for all imported stock. Fully equipped with modern inventory tracking, high-capacity shelving, and specialized areas for dry, chilled, and frozen products, this facility feeds our entire nationwide pipeline.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-[#18231D] mt-8 mb-3">2. Cold Chain Security</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Temperature control is critical in tropical island distribution. We maintain strict cold-chain security from the moment goods arrive in the port of Malé to their final delivery point. This ensures that premium dairy brands, beverages, and fresh goods retain their quality.
            </p>

            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-[#18231D] mt-8 mb-3">3. Archipelagic Maritime Freight</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We leverage an extensive network of local cargo vessels, cargo dhonis, and domestic shipping links to deliver merchandise. Our logistics desk coordinates directly with vessel captains to guarantee that orders are dispatched on schedule and reach regional island merchants intact.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- B2B CTA band inside page -->
          <div class="pt-8 border-t border-[#D8D4C9]/40 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 bg-[#DDEBE2]/30 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-[#083C2B] mb-1">Inquire About B2B Supply</h3>
              <p class="font-body text-xs text-[#566159] leading-relaxed">
                Connect with our logistics team to discuss custom cargo delivery terms.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 w-full md:w-auto shrink-0 justify-center">
              <a href="/request-quote" class="btn-primary">Request wholesale quote</a>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">General Contact</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: var(--color-green);
    color: var(--color-surface) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: none;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.16s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-green-dark);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--color-green) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-green);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.16s ease, color 0.16s ease;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-green);
    color: var(--color-surface) !important;
  }
</style>
